## ğŸ“„ File: `vercel.json`

```json
{
  "version": 2,
  "builds": [
    {
      "src": "package.json",
      "use": "@vercel/static-build",
      "config": {
        "distDir": "dist"
      }
    }
  ],
  "routes": [
    {
      "src": "/(.*)",
      "dest": "/index.html"
    }
  ],
  "env": {
    "REACT_APP_RPC_URL": "@rpc_url",
    "REACT_APP_PROGRAM_ID": "@program_id",
    "REACT_APP_TREASURY": "@treasury_address"
  }
}
```

