## ğŸ“‹ Checklist Before Launch

- [ ] Treasury address configured
- [ ] RPC endpoint tested (rate limits checked)
- [ ] Wallet connection working on mobile
- [ ] Transaction confirmation properly awaited
- [ ] Error messages user-friendly
- [ ] Bid increments enforced
- [ ] Patron messages sanitized (max 64 chars)
- [ ] Treasury balance updates after bids
- [ ] Patron hall fetches from on-chain data
- [ ] Responsive design tested on iPhone
- [ ] Solana Explorer links working

